{"tid":147772,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"勸大家咪食第一啖煙","createTime":"2017-03-08T05:57:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T05:29:07.000Z","uid":54581,"like":49,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6542f29ad2c668d0c79d967a8b95d7d596db005c","tid":147772,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T05:57:17.000Z","msg":"食左一包已經上上地癮<br />\n<br />\n依家個感覺就好似小佬仔想食糖咁<br />\n<br />\n唔食又唔會話好難頂好想食，非食不可<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過有時口痕就會想吸一兩支咁"},{"pid":"996a0bc756118523b7504b9d77f59de97fbd5426","tid":147772,"uid":54581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T05:59:04.000Z","msg":"細路仔<br />\n<br />\n屌食完兩支個頭wingwing地"},{"pid":"d332d8cfe75fbf302da49e39224324b91d3104bf","tid":147772,"uid":89608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T06:00:35.000Z","msg":"明知係有毒有害既野仲要去食, 真心ON9"},{"pid":"11cc70ff983cb41a6194c436fb56107edecec139","tid":147772,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T08:25:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73943f17bfcfe65294f4ec86ed4aee97ddbcdf19","tid":147772,"uid":10236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T08:29:47.000Z","msg":"想聽你吸煙的故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24039c105643f9815d838fda6cc9cc48838d7a6d","tid":147772,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:09:00.000Z","msg":"戒左奶未？"},{"pid":"62a252ed54a0df61d1c310de0f0d92f26be5e855","tid":147772,"uid":86893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:21:46.000Z","msg":"二手煙算唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e91a55328d8b7a6eacfb180e807aa1ada03d31f","tid":147772,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:39:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想聽你吸煙的故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我話有次走左巴士<br />\n嬲嬲地走去買包煙你信唔信"},{"pid":"7f6d78545b313dd8f4d389c18fadfaf50187aa35","tid":147772,"uid":31552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:41:40.000Z","msg":"其實我真係唔明點解會上癮，我小學既時候同個frd一日一包半（最高峰期），後黎上左中一就好少食，再到中二已經無食。<br />\n唔明點解成日有人話介唔到乜乜乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf39ebb4ce02d3826bc917d2fc6857b8409881a","tid":147772,"uid":26200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:52:19.000Z","msg":"同食曾生薯片一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ab5c21191014bf2d481bcf71c5e4a211412f08","tid":147772,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:58:18.000Z","msg":"食多過5枝都已經肚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958f9d99fb6f226afddf8e654f5df5f4bc341b16","tid":147772,"uid":89964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T11:40:04.000Z","msg":"一包=一啖okokok"},{"pid":"e3934dbe90e2b5490714f97cd29e25ad9bad45c9","tid":147772,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:03:37.000Z","msg":"返工放煙break食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d124b3e71eafbba7e05159e60e092f17ad356fc9","tid":147772,"uid":58551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:07:48.000Z","msg":"wing wing地就唔好食喇<br />\n你重未上癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5108c57435c0e0da0f0308e34a71656c5df95d6b","tid":147772,"uid":13382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:10:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>wing wing地就唔好食喇<br />\n你重未上癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但就係想要wingwing 地個感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbd21b21b090d202659559417ee7845a92fb915e","tid":147772,"uid":4213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:18:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">煙鏟死全家<br />\n煙撚生Cancer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"0029ac86d1786496912dc05e7cb6339205906023","tid":147772,"uid":36829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:23:04.000Z","msg":"我覺得根本無必要介，食落開心咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我自己就5年煙齡，食得唔多平均兩日一包，無諗過介煙，落酒吧一晚一包都試過，但又可以控制到自己唔食幾日都得，純粹係心癮。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a073f43b5f22d80fd6a25a50cbb2aee4f9edc660","tid":147772,"uid":55997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:14:59.000Z","msg":"未食過千奇唔好食<br />\n因為你想像唔到佢有幾難戒<br />\n利申:已戒"},{"pid":"42fbb579edd7284d3456b36f52b72460e57ab101","tid":147772,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:27:46.000Z","msg":"樓主渣ga <br />\n已戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95b800940e845ffa59a031d9fda4c11464026bad","tid":147772,"uid":1065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:37:00.000Z","msg":"由你食第一枝煙開始已經返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食左一枝已經有機會影響到你DNA<br />\n之後生唔生cancer都係睇彩數<br />\n戒左都一樣<br />\n唔戒易中招啲咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46551fb4d8e2dc6f39891a7f967d9ced5113d5e8","tid":147772,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:40:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7a7ffab96fd9050b5653be31d12467657455f365","tid":147772,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:50:47.000Z","msg":"收皮啦"},{"pid":"2ee11271d3e1dd48b452e404cd42166cf97b658a","tid":147772,"uid":28201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:53:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未食過千奇唔好食<br />\n因為你想像唔到佢有幾難戒<br />\n利申:已戒</blockquote><br />\n農夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3e6ab71cf6ce4ab5a2fb70bb8158a47455bbc0","tid":147772,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:55:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"23a55b07dd5611ad301610a56172c945e15b08b0","tid":147772,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:55:41.000Z","msg":"如果雪茄呢?近排試左"},{"pid":"26421b28d5c73261db7368716cd1452a4555025c","tid":147772,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:58:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>由你食第一枝煙開始已經返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食左一枝已經有機會影響到你DNA<br />\n之後生唔生cancer都係睇彩數<br />\n戒左都一樣<br />\n唔戒易中招啲咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁唔食煙生唔生cancer都係睇彩數</blockquote><br />\n你可以咁安慰自己, 不過食煙嘅生cancer機會比唔食嘅高好多咁解"},{"pid":"6adc999133377b862f31f8947025d7ef62b34c12","tid":147772,"uid":60535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:58:26.000Z","msg":"中三試過半枝，feel到陣癮，即停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 由細到大都不停屌柒我老豆老母食煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點知最近發近埋我細佬都開始食，準備開佢波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d41b2c56bfc20c612f16e5bf610c8c01095ab14c","tid":147772,"uid":19520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:58:31.000Z","msg":"返工同事有食 貪得意就食<br />\n計埋淨係食左5枝就無再食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n純粹係to do list想做既一樣野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f2b31e24d5ecef104c51db65ff7f3e4efd22d60","tid":147772,"uid":14961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:07:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">煙鏟死全家<br />\n煙撚生Cancer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote><br />\n逼人食二手煙既全部生癌死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d532575d8a61d55e9abb6dcd699ae052699ac8f","tid":147772,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:08:47.000Z","msg":"食過幾次，完全無意慾想再食，每次食完都好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2faf3f9dd7f1333ceacce13d524d7628c84c6b4","tid":147772,"uid":89840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:10:07.000Z","msg":"反煙撚仲煩閪d婦團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce89d3e2d32f3281443fa8134a4204deea67693","tid":147772,"uid":18864,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:11:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反煙撚仲煩閪d婦團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食煙撚咪又係一條自私撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18d3e6614a805fb5e4a012cd05d85c8bc6c68370","tid":147772,"uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:12:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果雪茄呢?近排試左</blockquote><br />\n雪茄係個口度浪 唔係扯肺"},{"pid":"93b341a9257932eb53ba658b0415a18b2a51961d","tid":147772,"uid":19502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:14:29.000Z","msg":"斷斷續續食左半年 頭三個月係無啦啦想食<br />\n但食左一枝都wingwing地又想嘔<br />\n但又有條癮想食 個陣可能3日先食一兩枝煙<br />\n隔左一個月又突然間想食<br />\n點知扯左入肺都無wing無想嘔 就中意左食<br />\n不過我係屋企三日可以唔食<br />\n但一出街就一定要食<br />\n算唔算係上左癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804691423f18b6962b3cc60c7885f1b54fb77ebf","tid":147772,"uid":19502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:17:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">返工同事有食 貪得意就食</span><br />\n計埋淨係食左5枝就無再食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n純粹係to do list想做既一樣野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係因為咁先食第一枝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec2d6eb1565b8e94bfee975d06100e8daae3234e","tid":147772,"uid":35080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:26:48.000Z","msg":"細個幼稚園個陣<br />\n家姐拎老豆啲煙<br />\n幫我點埋火比我吃<br />\n我吃第一口煙咳到仆街<br />\n之後都無再吃過一手煙"},{"pid":"1b616131544acd11f1df43491b8920eb4827eac3","tid":147772,"uid":26406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:29:42.000Z","msg":"買過包 半年食左4支 有時心思思都忍到"},{"pid":"a9ad625637852c0aeb246a2032321deefda4e09f","tid":147772,"uid":11915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:37:43.000Z","msg":"有咩方法可以wing番 個種感覺好撚正"},{"pid":"3be805827c5fc542940aecab4cfc378c9f22f572","tid":147772,"uid":79093,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:49:37.000Z","msg":"吸過一兩啖 但無上癮 唔明上癮既位係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n比較鐘意睇住板煙就咁燒 得閒先吸一啖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\nbtw 人終須一死 吸煙影響健康呢啲同自己既快樂點樣比較啊 <br />\n哦 我比著你呢一世都健健康康 但唔開心咁過生活好咩 <br />\n對於生死就睇開啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁執著仲痛苦"},{"pid":"3578e8178c6c1ee0d381e34896afae05686176da","tid":147772,"uid":33851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:50:53.000Z","msg":"食過幾枝就會有心癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca9b4406cdf0dc881afd45ce51335625306b479b","tid":147772,"uid":72796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:56:43.000Z","msg":"已經食左仲有冇得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔想死住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"097d603c411b8ac59b111c303e8559a0d469bcde","tid":147772,"uid":13158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:57:07.000Z","msg":"食過一支係會上癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但比人阻止就唔會再食"},{"pid":"751ee504f3880c4692f773cb3f6ed979e9dc5014","tid":147772,"uid":61712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:59:28.000Z","msg":"10定12歲好奇心食過一次<br />\n難頂到掉地下 再掃入垃圾桶<br />\n完<br />\n唔會食 好撚臭"},{"pid":"dbae1d8c38afd94eac55ca9fde148b9577eb4af4","tid":147772,"uid":84270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:01:18.000Z","msg":"樓主食煙個樣實好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n濕撚曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ddf8e551236f389724143d8e76b1fdf2ba91f7a","tid":147772,"uid":19837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:01:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩方法可以wing番 個種感覺好撚正</blockquote><br />\n24小時唔食煙<br />\n然後第2日企定定大啖大啖咁扯"},{"pid":"9626498688094deebd6780c4e10af6f5e217afc4","tid":147772,"uid":1818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:03:29.000Z","msg":"第一次食<br />\n坐個露台<br />\n聽住借火<br />\n無記錯第一次已經係藍莓8<br />\n咳撚到仆街<br />\n手都震埋<br />\n又wing<br />\n但幾正<br />\n就冇食過了"},{"pid":"764f7feb585dd552e6acdbb6d28ecc3e555c160c","tid":147772,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:03:44.000Z","msg":"食過幾支 冇wing冇上癮 可能唔識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caeabd3b0852599138405bd78ac98cd0b96d07b2","tid":147772,"uid":55249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:05:02.000Z","msg":"有親人肺癌死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢食開煙嘅<br />\n食煙，不了"},{"pid":"82ee4fe14a9226b6feead6c704c66dc8ba71d003","tid":147772,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:05:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食過幾支 冇wing冇上癮 可能唔識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係我呀哥細佬就愈食愈大癮 一日兩包 十分鐘就要食一支"},{"pid":"146583faab9bf7dcda58d1f5de9862d2e57083fd","tid":147772,"uid":55002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:06:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個幼稚園個陣<br />\n家姐拎老豆啲煙<br />\n幫我點埋火比我吃<br />\n我吃第一口煙咳到仆街<br />\n之後都無再吃過一手煙</blockquote><br />\n想識你家姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a3550f357c23a8052d92e0b74acb73d2c61416c","tid":147772,"uid":35946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:14:03.000Z","msg":"真係奉勸大家唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />見到公公而家好辛苦覺得真係好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n公公以前食煙，我地勸左好多次都勸唔到佢戒，睇住佢食到而家想食都冇氣食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家佢講兩句野、行過去廁所就好似唔夠氣咁，平時又要用力吸先抖到氣，所以有時訓訓下會抖唔到氣要入醫院，最近嗰次入左醫院兩個幾星期，而家轉左去療養院，仲未出得返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢膝頭又磨蝕哂軟骨，原本可以換膝蓋嗰啲，但係醫生話佢喺手術其間有機會抖唔到氣，驚有生命危險，所以又做唔到。雖然當中係有年老嘅原因啦，但係佢食煙食壞左個肺都係一個原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係話食親煙都實會咁，但係一日唔戒煙，啲煙都係整壞梗你個肺。見到食壞左個肺嘅人真係好辛苦，希望大家唔好步佢後塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8fae4376e1daa511fd8fb188d69bdfaf99492b8","tid":147772,"uid":35946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:16:41.000Z","msg":"打咁長篇文唔好意思，就當俾我發洩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0ca12f25c100bbdc56ff8a8feaecc04f309583","tid":147772,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:21:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由你食第一枝煙開始已經返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食左一枝已經有機會影響到你DNA<br />\n之後生唔生cancer都係睇彩數<br />\n戒左都一樣<br />\n唔戒易中招啲咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好老實，唔係話幫煙撚平反定點<br />\n<br />\n其實啲人食二手煙，水煙其實仲傷好多倍<br />\n<br />\n我諗大部份人唔多唔少都吸過二手煙<br />\n<br />\n咁咪大家都仆街?<br />\n<br />\nbtw,有醫學證明你介煙後，身體係會recover的"},{"pid":"96a4fa124159867ebc014732b3068549d65e099c","tid":147772,"uid":39785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:31:07.000Z","msg":"好臭呀你"},{"pid":"c9af71bf056db7637aa851abe5315c335264a6cd","tid":147772,"uid":14716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:37:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由你食第一枝煙開始已經返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食左一枝已經有機會影響到你DNA<br />\n之後生唔生cancer都係睇彩數<br />\n戒左都一樣<br />\n唔戒易中招啲咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食香蕉都會生cancer啦咁講<br />\n蕉有radioactive 嘅物質"},{"pid":"0a46a026246e3b1025a71fd7bbaa996b7b193754","tid":147772,"uid":88507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:39:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買過包 半年食左4支 有時心思思都忍到</blockquote><br />\n包煙仲食得嘅？潮晒喇"},{"pid":"e70168a104724ed5dcecaecdec5cf14bdcecc206","tid":147772,"uid":15660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:43:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反煙撚仲煩閪d婦團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAgger利申冇食過"},{"pid":"860d0fb8f11a5d612e2645fbcb5400729c97477a","tid":147772,"uid":79686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:43:46.000Z","msg":"食煙仆街過吸毒<br />\n<br />\n中意食唔仆街 上左癮唔仆街 死埋都唔仆街<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母吹撚左落我到呀死正仆街"},{"pid":"fbcad172ff9d84d6250180917779c5c7a6461bf7","tid":147772,"uid":14119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:44:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">煙鏟死全家<br />\n煙撚生Cancer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote><br />\n逼人食二手煙既全部生癌死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4c12e2cfb7848ea309e746eba0653b6966ecc90","tid":147772,"uid":4697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:47:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>斷斷續續食左半年 頭三個月係無啦啦想食<br />\n但食左一枝都wingwing地又想嘔<br />\n但又有條癮想食 個陣可能3日先食一兩枝煙<br />\n隔左一個月又突然間想食<br />\n點知扯左入肺都無wing無想嘔 就中意左食<br />\n不過我係屋企三日可以唔食<br />\n但一出街就一定要食<br />\n算唔算係上左癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同你好似，不過返工先食。 出街，屋企唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一包食到半個月多d<br />\n利申 地盤撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2edfa6b8a6e2ebf1590f775ea35c0db48a890551","tid":147772,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:48:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>由你食第一枝煙開始已經返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食左一枝已經有機會影響到你DNA<br />\n之後生唔生cancer都係睇彩數<br />\n戒左都一樣<br />\n唔戒易中招啲咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食香蕉都會生cancer啦咁講<br />\n蕉有radioactive 嘅物質</blockquote><br />\n呃你有寶咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/news/health-37849000\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fhealth-37849000&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=261f5ac0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fhealth-37849000&h=aa2849e1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.com/news/health-37849000</a>"},{"pid":"f8f02ce597b161fcdb61a20f4267ec25efadb8c7","tid":147772,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:50:50.000Z","msg":"試完好收手啦，本人對煙民無乜感覺，除非佢對住我噴就會屌7佢，不過而家眼見好多都企埋一邊食"},{"pid":"d2d043bcf8632391260c647aaf79c5626be1e6c0","tid":147772,"uid":29187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:52:16.000Z","msg":"日日食真係停唔到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n二手煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全家得我唔食，屋企人從來都冇諗過戒"},{"pid":"705e4dd89a9c2deaa5920648c54770a9e37c3393","tid":147772,"uid":2899,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:53:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>由你食第一枝煙開始已經返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食左一枝已經有機會影響到你DNA<br />\n之後生唔生cancer都係睇彩數<br />\n戒左都一樣<br />\n唔戒易中招啲咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好老實，唔係話幫煙撚平反定點<br />\n<br />\n其實啲人食二手煙，水煙其實仲傷好多倍<br />\n<br />\n我諗大部份人唔多唔少都吸過二手煙<br />\n<br />\n咁咪大家都仆街?<br />\n<br />\nbtw,有醫學證明你介煙後，身體係會recover的</blockquote><br />\n就係最新嘅研究話第一下就會damage到DNA<br />\n戒左都一樣<br />\nRecover返嘅係某啲機能<br />\n但因為DNA損壞所引發嘅癌症機會係逆轉唔到"},{"pid":"3c51079ddf9861383079b5f2a28d4c74cb62cb68","tid":147772,"uid":5497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:54:03.000Z","msg":"我係想食就食，想唔食就唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 壓力大果排會想食，但只限係街先食，係